---
title: Italian Chicken Stew with Orzo and Fresh Basil
description: Inspired by the Italian classic minestrone, this stew gets a filling upgrade with the addition of shredded roast chicken. A final flourish of Parmesan is the perfect finishing touch to this hearty and warm weeknight meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-poulet-a-litalienne-0846e1be.jpg
